1953;;Last of the Comanches;;American;;Andre de Toth;;Broderick Crawford, Barbara Hale;;western;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Last_of_the_Comanches;;Sgt. Matt Trainor (Broderick Crawford) leads the survivors of a massacred cavalry troop from the ruins of the destroyed frontier town of Dry Buttes, along with a ragtag group of stagecoach passengers, in a fight for survival against fierce Comanches led by Black Cloud (John War Eagle) at a desert ruin.